title: Arsenal Legends - Dennis Bergkamp
description:
Over the course of it's history Arsenal Football club has seen many players come and go, but very few can be defined as Legends. In this series the finest players ever to pull on the famous red and white shirt tell us their Arsenal story in their own words. Featuring Dennis Bergkamp, Thierry Henry, Martin Keown and Lee Dixon series one of 'Arsenal Legends' will provide the ultimate re-telling of some of football's most famous personal journeys using archive footage and exclusive interview content. Powerful and honest, this unique series provides a fresh insight into the very few Arsenal players who can truly be counted as Legends.

Quality: 720p
